AREA - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-ospf-oper:ospf/processes/process/{process-name}/default-vrf/areas/area/{area-id}/

Retrieve operation of resource: area

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

area-id: string
in path

ID of area-id

200 OK
area_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

DATABASE-AREAS - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-ospf-oper:ospf/processes/process/{process-name}/default-vrf/database/database-areas/

Retrieve operation of resource: database-areas

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

200 OK
database-areas_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

DATABASE-AREA - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-ospf-oper:ospf/processes/process/{process-name}/default-vrf/database/database-areas/database-area/{area-id}/

Retrieve operation of resource: database-area

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

area-id: string
in path

ID of area-id

200 OK
database-area_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

LSA-HEADER - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-ospf-oper:ospf/processes/process/{process-name}/default-vrf/database/database-areas/database-area/{area-id}/lsas/lsa/lsa-header/

Retrieve operation of resource: lsa-header

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

area-id: string
in path

ID of area-id

200 OK
lsa-header_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK) 
{
  
"lsa-header": {Header information

    
"lsa-age": "integer", LSA's Age (s)

    
"lsid": "string", LS ID

    
"checksum": "integer", Checksum value

    
"dn-age-lsa": "boolean", If true, Do Not Age this LSA

    
"advertising-router": "string", Router ID of Advertising Router

    
"nsf": "boolean", If true,  LSA received from neighbor during NSF

    
"ls-type": "string", LSA type

    
"sequence-number": "integer", Current Sequence number

    
"lsa-area-id": "string" Area ID in decimal or dotted-decimal format

  }
}

    },

"second-table-index": "integer", Second table index

"last-inst-minute-table-index": "integer" Last Minute table index processed

    },

    },

"acknowledgement": "boolean", If true, the reason not to delete this LSA is\nbecause it's Acknowledgement list is not empty

  }
